OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772733967
OL,3,CMP's call for freeze on season tickets
OL,4,Cprices to 'put supporters first'
OL,6,FA group of MPs have raised concerns
OL,7,Fover clubs increasing their ticket
OL,8,Fprices to their most loyal fans,
OL,9,Fwarning it creates "an existential
OL,10,Fthreat" to the culture and community
OL,11,Fof football.
OL,13,FAn Early Day Motion (EDM) on ticket
OL,14,Fpricing has been tabled by Liverpool
OL,15,FWest Derby MP Ian Byrne and has 16
OL,16,Fsignatories.
OL,18,FThe EDM urges clubs to engage with
OL,19,Fsupporters on pricing, stating:
OL,20,F"Football without fans is nothing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
