OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772733967
OL,3,CMP's call for freeze on season tickets
OL,4,Cprices to 'put supporters first'
OL,6,F"This House raises serious concerns at
OL,7,Fthe trend of annual ticket price
OL,8,Fincreases for Premier League football,
OL,9,Fas highlighted by the Football
OL,10,FSupporters' Association Stop
OL,11,FExploiting Loyalty campaign; believes
OL,12,Fworking class and young supporters are
OL,13,Fbeing priced out; fears that squeezing
OL,14,Flocal and dedicated fans poses an
OL,15,Fexistential threat to the culture and
OL,16,Fcommunity of football."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
