PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772733967
OL,3,CMP's call for freeze on season tickets
OL,4,Cprices to 'put supporters first'
OL,6,FThe FSA has called on Premier League
OL,7,Fclubs to freeze ticket prices for the
OL,8,Fupcoming season, but Arsenal have
OL,9,Falready decided to increase prices by
OL,10,F3.9% for 2026-27.
OL,12,FLabour MP Ian Byrne has urged
OL,13,FLiverpool and Everton to freeze prices
OL,14,Fand "lead the way putting supporters
OL,15,Ffirst in a city where one-third of
OL,16,Ffamilies face food insecurity".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
