PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772733967
OL,3,CMP's call for freeze on season tickets
OL,4,Cprices to 'put supporters first'
OL,6,FThe text said it was "misleading" for
OL,7,Fclubs to blame inflation for price
OL,8,Fincreases, particularly set against
OL,9,Fthe current domestic television deal
OL,10,Fbeing worth #6.7 billion over four
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FThe FSA and the Premier League have
OL,14,Fbeen contacted for comment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
