PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772733967
OL,3,CMP's call for freeze on season tickets
OL,4,Cprices to 'put supporters first'
OL,6,FThe FSA has called on Premier League
OL,7,Fclubs to freeze season ticket prices
OL,8,Ffor next season as part of its
OL,9,F'Protect the Fans, Protect the Game'
OL,10,Finitiative, but Arsenal have already
OL,11,Fdecided to increase prices by 3.9 per
OL,12,Fcent for 2026-27 along with
OL,13,Fintroducing a new Category A+ ticket,
OL,14,Fa change cited in the EDM.
OL,16,FThe EDM tabled by the Labour MP urged
OL,17,FLiverpool and Everton to freeze prices
OL,18,Fand "lead the way putting supporters
OL,19,Ffirst in a city where one-third of
OL,20,Ffamilies face food insecurity".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
